<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.4.9">
<l>veñcuṭariṟ ṟāṉaṭumāl. vīṅkiruḷiṉ nuṇṭuḷiyā</l>
<l>yañcuṭara veyyō ṉaṇineṭuntēr tōṉṟātāl</l>
<l>ceñcuṭart tāmaraikkaṇ celvaṉum vārāṉāl</l>
<l>neñciṭartīrp pāriṉiyār niṉṟuruku kiṉṟēṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like the [sun’s] hot glow it will kill [me]. As fine drops of swelling darkness,</l>
<l>the decorated long chariot of the Kot one with pretty glow doesn’t show.</l>
<l>The lord with red-glowing lotus eyes will not come.</l>
<l>Who will end [my] heart’s affliction now? I stand [and] dissolve.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
